{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1665882365.8162522", "card_id": "EV_12219283", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 0}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "直播：二十大「党代表通道」开启"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-72fb2ff0915ade85494fa07ec13fad60_1440w.jpeg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "1207 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/theater/74689"}, "text_tag_area": {"text": "正在直播", "font_color": "GYL01A", "background": "GYL01A"}}, "attached_info": "Cm4Ix8mXpKz5yfUoEBgaBDY5ODUgr5etmgZAAHIIMTIyMTkyODN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZMoBI2h0dHBzOi8vd3d3LnpoaWh1LmNvbS90aGVhdGVyLzc0Njg58gETCAESD2RvbWFpbl9vcGVyYXRvcg=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1665882365.8170009", "card_id": "AT_573964576", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 0}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "二十大新闻发布会，回应了这些热点问题"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "党的二十大召开在即，党的二十大新闻发布会今天下午举行。在介绍大会有关情况后，二十大新闻发言人孙业礼回答了记者提出的多个热点问题。 谈小康：成色应该说是十足的 现在看，我们已经建成的小康社会远远超出了改革开放之初的预想，达到了党的十八大提出的目标…"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-2636abbbc071ff35d06e1733487b161d_1440w.webp"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "721 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "link": {"url": "https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/573964576"}}, "attached_info": "ClYIx8mXpKz5yfUoEAcaCTIxNTY4MDUzNSCJ4qqaBii2ATAgQAFyCTU3Mzk2NDU3NngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA8gETCAESD2RvbWFpbl9vcGVyYXRvcg=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "2_1665882365.819433", "card_id": "ZV_1564686244298248193", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 0}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "党的二十大新闻发言人：统一有好处，「台独」是绝路，外人靠不住"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "中国共产党第二十次全国代表大会新闻发布会 2022 年 10 月 15 日在人民大会堂举行。\n 二十大发言人回答记者提问时指出，关于台湾问题，但凡有一线和平解决可能，我们将付